text: Swathi Chinukulu (Telugu: స్వాతిచినుకులు) is an Indian Telugu Language soap opera that airs on ETV Telugu. It premiered on 9 September 2013. It airs from Monday to Saturday at 8:00 pm (IST). It has completed 2126 episodes (as of 19 september 2020). == Plot == Mythili and Neelaveni are two young women with a strong bond. They live vastly different lives in opposite ends of the world and go through various struggles. Mythili a Joyous young lady has been migrated to Europe for job. Her vibrant experiences with her boss Panigrahi and his way made her fell in love with him. Neelaveni a village girl born and brought up among sentimental relationships struggling with her love feel. The story deals about these two ladies experiences and lives. == Cast == * Sithara as Tulasi * Rachana as Neelaveni * Rachitha Mahalakshmi as Nila (former cast) (died in serial) * Neha Gowda as Mythili * Harikrishna as Paanigrahi * Sindhura Darshanam * Aadarsh * Siddharth Varma *Kavitha Gowda * Preeti * Ramyakrishnan * Vanisree * Sharath Banu * Branden Garrett == References == == External links == *Swathi Chinukulu on IMDb Category:Telugu-language television shows Category:2013 Indian television series debuts Category:Indian television soap operas
